# AI Image Signature Looks

When generating AI images (via image tools or prompts), **all signature looks must be highly exaggerated**.

- Push distinctive style cues hard: silhouette, proportions, color contrast, texture, lighting, and motif.
- Prefer bold, unmistakable caricature of the look over subtle or photoreal restraint.
- If a style, brand aesthetic, era, or character trait is specified, amplify it until it reads instantly at a glance.
- Avoid muted, tasteful, or understated interpretations unless the user explicitly asks for restraint.
